<package name="openexr" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>Utilities for work with HDR images in OpenEXR format</title>
  <description>OpenEXR is a high dynamic-range (HDR) image file format developed by
Industrial Light &amp; Magic for use in computer imaging applications. This package
contains a set of utilities to work with this format.

* exrheader, a utility for dumping header information
* exrstdattr, a utility for modifying OpenEXR standard attributes
* exrmaketiled, for generating tiled and rip/mipmapped images
* exrenvmap, for creating OpenEXR environment maps
* exrmakepreview, for creating preview images for OpenEXR files
* exr2aces, converter to ACES format
* exrmultiview, combine two or more images into one multi-view</description>
  <devel project="graphics" package="openexr"/>
</package>
